            </rs>.</p>
               <p>LAWRENCE - <rs id="t18190113-34-verdict207" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190113-34-verdict207" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Holroyd.</p>
